title: Ep. - 306 - LIZZIE GRUBMAN FROM MTV’S POWER GIRLS REAL HOUSEWIVES OF SALT LAKE CITY REVIEW
description:
Lizzie Grubman from MTV’s 2005 reality TV series about press maven Lizzie mentoring a team of young hopeful publicists as they work their way in the world of celebrities, glamour and public relations to ultimately earn a permanent spot on her team.

 

Abby and Vanessa, co-hosts of from Real Moms of Bravo podcast and Danny Murphy from Not Another True Crime Podcast review the season premiere of Bravo’s Real Housewives of Salt Lake City.
